com.davidbracewell.hermes.annotator

Class FuzzyLexiconAnnotator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.davidbracewell.hermes.annotator.SentenceLevelAnnotator
      • com.davidbracewell.hermes.annotator.ViterbiAnnotator
        • com.davidbracewell.hermes.annotator.FuzzyLexiconAnnotator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Annotator, Serializable

    public class FuzzyLexiconAnnotator
extends ViterbiAnnotator

    A lexicon annotator that allows gaps to occur in multi-word expressions. For example, "old red car" and "old broke car" would match the lexicon item "old car" with a distance of one.

    Author:
    David B. Bracewell
    See Also:
